videos.headline: OU's Taylor Robertson sets NCAA D-I women's career 3-point record
videos.description: Oklahoma's Taylor Robertson hits her 498th career 3-pointer, setting an NCAA Division I women's basketball record.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (OU's Taylor Robertson sets NCAA D-I women's career 3-point record) 2023/01/28 ESHEET

videos.headline: Iowa State's Ashley Joens hits the corner trey
videos.description: Ashley Joens spots up and nails a corner 3 to cut into the Sooners' lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Iowa State's Ashley Joens hits the corner trey) 2023/01/28 ESHEET

videos.headline: Ashley Joens stays hot from downtown to retake the lead
